<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4749120>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Cnemaspis uttaraghati sp. nov. (holotype, NRC-AA-1122): (A) dorsal view of body, (B) ventral view of body, (C) dorsal view of tail, and (D) ventral view of tail. Scale bars 10 mm; photos by Akshay Khandekar." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4749120/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4749124>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Cnemaspis uttaraghati sp. nov. (holotype, NRC-AA-1122), dorsal view of head (A), ventral view of head (B), lateral view of head (C), view of cloacal region showing femoral pores and post cloacal spurs (D), ventral view of right manus (E), and ventral view of right pes (F). Scale bars 5 mm; photos by Akshay Khandekar." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4749124/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4749126>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Details at mid-body of Cnemaspis uttaraghati sp. nov. (holotype, NRC-AA-1122): (A) dorsal view and (B) ventral view. Scale bars 5 mm; photos by Akshay Khandekar." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4749126/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4749132>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Cnemaspis uttaraghati sp. nov. in life: (A) male, holotype NRC-AA-1122, (B) female, paratype NRC-AA-1123, and (C) female, paratype BNHS 2800; photos by Tejas Thackeray." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4749132/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4749134>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Type series of Cnemaspis uttaraghati sp. nov. from left to right: BNHS 2799, NRC-AA-1123 and BNHS 2800. Scale bar 10 mm; photos by Akshay Khandekar." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4749134/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4749114>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Elevation map showing type localities of Cnemaspis spp. distributed in the northern Western Ghats: 1, Cnemaspis uttaraghati sp. nov.; 2, C. mahabali; 3, C. ajijae; 4, C. girii; 5, C. koynaensis; 6, C. amba; 7, C. kolhapurensis; 8, C. limayei; 9, C. ranganaensis; 10, C. amboliensis and C. flaviventralis; 11, C. goaensis; 12, C. indraneildasii. Prepared by Ishan Agarwal." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4749114/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4749136>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. A) Habitat of Cnemaspis uttaraghati sp. nov. near Kedareshwar Caves on Harishchandragad, Ahmednagar district, Maharashtra state, India; B) entrance of one of the caves at type locality; C) hatched communal egg clutch with a single dark unhatched egg inside the cave; photos by Y. Satam." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4749136/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

